2. **Enchanted Mistress and Bewitched Servant**  
   - **Scenario**: You are an enchantress who has placed a spell on your servant. They must follow your commands or risk further magical consequences. Add layers of fantasy by creating tasks they must complete to “free” themselves from your spell.  
